readable.content: A girl in a pool wearing goggles and surrounded by other children A girl in green goggles in a pool with three other children . A red haired girl making a peace sign is wearing neon green glasses and floaties and playing in the pool with other kids . A red-headed girl offers the peace sign as she swims in the pool with floaties . A young girl with goggles and floaties poses for the camera as she plays in a pool .
